From 8d5cb830570aa3fa257cd9a93d163854c86b85a2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Robert Beckett <bob.beckett@collabora.com>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 18:48:33 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] script: Add System script plugin

Allow these scripts to get the system vendor and product-id.
This allows theme decsions based on the product it is running
on without having to hard code different themes.

Signed-off-by: Robert Beckett <bob.beckett@collabora.com>
---
